Brogrammers/
├── .github/
│   └── workflows/
│       ├── ci-cd.yml          # Main trigger (runs tests → triggers build & deploy)
│       ├── build.yml          # Build artifacts and upload (triggered by ci-cd)
│       └── deploy.yml         # Download artifact & deploy to Raspberry Pi (triggered by ci-cd)
├── deploy/
│   ├── build.sh              # Build artifacts script
│   └── deploy.sh             # Deployment script
└── (your source code)